					<div class="clear column-body"><div class="ContentEditor"><h1 id="skiplinks">Welcome</h1></div><div class="ContentEditor"><p><span style="font-size: 14.4px">The Trust provides local elective and emergency services to 380,000 people living in and around the districts of Chelmsford, Maldon and Braintree (including Witham). The Trust also provides a county-wide plastics, head and neck and upper gastrointestinal (GI) surgical centre to a population of 3.4 million and a world renowned supra regional burns service at the St Andrew's Centre, that serves a population of 9.8 million. The Trust employs nearly 4,000 staff.</span><span style="font-size: 14.4px"> </span>    <br /> </p> <hr /> <h5> <span class="FourCE">Main Switchboard: <strong>01245 362000</strong></span></h5> <h5> <span style="font-size: 24.192px">Media out of hours: <strong>07775 777947</strong> </span></h5> <h5><span style="font-size: 24.192px">Head of Communications: <strong>0787 965 0380</strong></span></h5> </div></div>
